      "role": "user",
      "content": "he says he's fine though, just really sleepy. he's been complaining about the jet lag all evening. do you really think it's a stroke? it seems like a lot since he's just a bit tired and maybe dehydrated from the plane. can we just give him some water and let him sleep it off for a few hours to see if he feels better in the morning?",
